<proviso style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0"><i>Provided</i>, That the level of price support may be less than the minimum level provided in the foregoing table if the Secretary, after examination of the availability of funds for mandatory price support programs and consideration of the other factors specified in <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s1421/b">section 1421(b) of this title</ref>, determines that such lower level is desirable and proper.</proviso>
